2014: Earned exempt status by finishing T9 at PGA TOUR Canada's Canada Qualifying School as an amateurâ€¦In PGA TOUR Canada debut, at the season-opening PC Financial Open, closed with a 5-under-par 67 to finish T7.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Won three events at St. John's, the 2013 Puma-Xavier Invitational, the 2014 Snowman Getaway and the 2014 Big East Championship...Was a 2012-13 Academic All-American...Helped the Red Storm to a team title at the 2014 Big East Championship.
tourBios.personal: Favorite athlete to watch is Matt Kuchar...Dream foursome would include Jack Nicklaus, Ben Hogan and Bobby Jones...Favorite course is Quaker Ridge GC...Favorite professional team is the New York Giants...Twitter name is @McCormick_Ryan.
